            <td>Focus on full range of motion and glute contraction at the top.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Bulgarian Split Squat</td>
            <td>3</td>
            <td>10 (each leg)</td>
            <td>Keep your torso upright and engage your glutes throughout the movement.</td>
